<br>
first you bind yourself in n freeport in the nw corner <br>
have the druid bind there too <br>
goto bb pull pegleg to to the druid rings kill him to spawn A lesser spirit have the chanter charm him to keep him there and make you indiferent <br>
then you say to the lesser spirit &quot;I wish to know more&quot; <br>
